description: The SPDR FTSE International Government Inflation-Protected Bond ETF seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, correspond generally to the price and yield performance of FTSE International Inflation-Linked Securities Select Index (the “Index”)Seeks to provide exposure to inflation-linked bonds of developed and emerging market countries outside of the USSeek to hedge against the erosion of purchasing power due to inflation outside of the U.S.Rebalanced on the last business day of the month
name: SPDR FTSE International Government Inflation-Protected Bond ETF
